dicates apical denticles on claw extremely higher than the others (Gen. A.) Char. 104." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3786800" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3786800/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="273">
